        <p><strong>Repair:</strong> Quoted both paths honestly. Repair (full tub assembly + labor): $1,180. Replacement: comparable WF45 around $1,000-$1,200. Customer chose repair given the matching DV dryer was still working perfectly and they wanted to keep the laundry stack matched.</p>
